preference.name: SNAPSHOT_OverideFolderHasPrecedence
preference.preference_description: IR#10129450 (P2) A Solution Proposal to the Incident Report Provided- PSE- remove precise on auto revision rule of snapshot By default it is not set at all and hence false. If this preference is not set to true, the original behavior will continue. To get the changed behavior SNAPSHOT_OverideFolderHasPrecedence has to be set to true
